" Minimum vim setup for the Gauntlet tutorial.
"
" The first two lines are the M-series Mac + Tahoe workaround:
" without them, syntax highlighting silently fails to load on
" some setups. Keeping the workaround in this fixture is a small
" demonstration of why context-as-fixture is useful — write the
" environment fix once, every story that runs vim picks it up.

set regexpengine=2
syntax enable

set number
filetype plugin indent on
